VYHY DBUr-YHVH 'aLY L'aMUr.
MH-LKM 'aThM MShLYM 'aTh-HMShL HZH 'yL-'aDMTh YShUr'aL L'aMUr 'aBVTh Y'aKLV BSUr VShNY HBNYM ThQHYNH.
ChY-'aNY N'aM 'aDNY YHVH 'aM-YHYH LKM 'yVD MShL HMShL HZH BYShUr'aL.
HN KL-HNPhShVTh LY HNH KNPhSh H'aB VKNPhSh HBN LY-HNH HNPhSh HChT'aTh HY'a ThMVTh.
V'aYSh KY-YHYH TShDYQ V'yShH MShPhT VTShDQH.
'aL-HHUrYM L'a 'aKL V'yYNYV L'a NSh'a 'aL-GLVLY BYTh YShUr'aL V'aTh-'aShTh Ur'yHV L'a TM'a V'aL-'aShH NDH L'a YQUrB.
V'aYSh L'a YVNH ChBLThV ChVB YShYB GZLH L'a YGZL LChMV LUr'yB YThN V'yYUrM YKSH-BGD.
BNShK L'a-YThN VThUrBYTh L'a YQCh M'yVL YShYB YDV MShPhT 'aMTh Y'yShH BYN 'aYSh L'aYSh.
BChQVThY YHLK VMShPhTY ShMUr L'yShVTh 'aMTh TShDYQ HV'a ChYH YChYH N'aM 'aDNY YHVH.
VHVLYD BN-PhUrYTSh ShPhK DM V'yShH 'aCh M'aChD M'aLH.
VHV'a 'aTh-KL-'aLH L'a 'yShH KY GM 'aL-HHUrYM 'aKL V'aTh-'aShTh Ur'yHV TM'a.
'yNY V'aBYVN HVNH GZLVTh GZL ChBL L'a YShYB V'aL-HGLVLYM NSh'a 'yYNYV ThV'yBH 'yShH.
BNShK NThN VThUrBYTh LQCh VChY L'a YChYH 'aTh KL-HThV'yBVTh H'aLH 'yShH MVTh YVMTh DMYV BV YHYH.
VHNH HVLYD BN VYUr'a 'aTh-KL-ChT'aTh 'aBYV 'aShUr 'yShH VYUr'aH VL'a Y'yShH KHN.
'yL-HHUrYM L'a 'aKL V'yYNYV L'a NSh'a 'aL-GLVLY BYTh YShUr'aL 'aTh-'aShTh Ur'yHV L'a TM'a.
V'aYSh L'a HVNH ChBL L'a ChBL VGZLH L'a GZL LChMV LUr'yB NThN V'yUrVM KSH- BGD.
M'yNY HShYB YDV NShK VThUrBYTh L'a LQCh MShPhTY 'yShH BChQVThY HLK HV'a L'a YMVTh B'yVN 'aBYV ChYH YChYH.
'aBYV KY-'yShQ 'yShQ GZL GZL 'aCh V'aShUr L'a-TVB 'yShH BThVK 'yMYV VHNH-MTh B'yVNV.
V'aMUrThM MD'y L'a-NSh'a HBN B'yVN H'aB VHBN MShPhT VTShDQH 'yShH 'aTh KL- ChQVThY ShMUr VY'yShH 'aThM ChYH YChYH.
HNPhSh HChT'aTh HY'a ThMVTh BN L'a-YSh'a B'yVN H'aB V'aB L'a YSh'a B'yVN HBN TShDQTh HTShDYQ 'yLYV ThHYH VUrSh'yTh UrSh'y 'yLYV ThHYH.
VHUrSh'y KY YShVB MKL-ChT'aThV 'aShUr 'yShH VShMUr 'aTh-KL-ChQVThY V'yShH MShPhT VTShDQH ChYH YChYH L'a YMVTh.
KL-PhSh'yYV 'aShUr 'yShH L'a YZKUrV LV BTShDQThV 'aShUr-'yShH YChYH.
HChPhTSh 'aChPhTSh MVTh UrSh'y N'aM 'aDNY YHVH HLV'a BShVBV MDUrKYV VChYH.
VBShVB TShDYQ MTShDQThV V'yShH 'yVL KKL HThV'yBVTh 'aShUr-'yShH HUrSh'y Y'yShH VChY KL-TShDQThV 'aShUr-'yShH L'a ThZKUrNH BM'yLV 'aShUr-M'yL VBChT'aThV 'aShUr-ChT'a BM YMVTh.
V'aMUrThM L'a YThKN DUrK 'aDNY ShM'yV-N'a BYTh YShUr'aL HDUrKY L'a YThKN HL'a DUrKYKM L'a YThKNV.
BShVB-TShDYQ MTShDQThV V'yShH 'yVL VMTh 'yLYHM B'yVLV 'aShUr-'yShH YMVTh.
VBShVB UrSh'y MUrSh'yThV 'aShUr 'yShH VY'ySh MShPhT VTShDQH HV'a 'aTh-NPhShV YChYH.
VYUr'aH VYShVB MKL-PhSh'yYV 'aShUr 'yShH ChYV YChYH L'a YMVTh.
V'aMUrV BYTh YShUr'aL L'a YThKN DUrK 'aDNY HDUrKY L'a YThKNV BYTh YShUr'aL HL'a DUrKYKM L'a YThKN.
LKN 'aYSh KDUrKYV 'aShPhT 'aThKM BYTh YShUr'aL N'aM 'aDNY YHVH ShVBV VHShYBV MKL-PhSh'yYKM VL'a-YHYH LKM LMKShVL 'yVN.
HShLYKV M'yLYKM 'aTh-KL-PhSh'yYKM 'aShUr PhSh'yThM BM V'yShV LKM LB ChDSh VUrVCh ChDShH VLMH ThMThV BYTh YShUr'aL.
KY L'a 'aChPhTSh BMVTh HMTh N'aM 'aDNY YHVH VHShYBV VChYV.
